1. Quick Pick - Easiest way to play -Press Quick Pick button and numbers will be generated randomly for you.
2. Play your own numbers -Select the numbers you want to play.
3. Check draw result Match all 10 of your numbers or 0 of your numbers to win the top prize ------------------------------------------- 0/12 $250,000 1/12 $500 2/12 $22 3/12 $7 4/12 $2 5/10 Free Play 8/12 $2 9/12 $7 10/12 $22 11/12 $500 12/12 $250,000
